metadata.name: Saturday Night's Alright (For Fighting) #14
metadata.description:
Ok, this is just for fun!
An NFT that changes every day based on the browser weekday.

The preview is generated accordingly, hence it will be different based on the day of the mint.

Control Keys:
- 0 -> Sunday
- 1 -> Monday
- 2 -> Tuesday
- 3 -> Wednesday
- 4 -> Thursday
- 5 -> Friday
- 6 -> Saturday!
- S -> save png
- H -> save high res png

metadata.name: Unicorn #780
metadata.description:
All of us have dreams, and everyone would like to meet a fairy, a genie, a wizard, or someone else who will make our dreams come true in a snap of a finger or with the wave of a wand. But we're the only ones who can do it. We are those magical unicorns, unique, inimitable, with our own qualities and magical abilities.
These unicorns are the visualization of our inner selves that makes our dreams come true. An embodiment of all the best with a huge positive magical power.

metadata.name: Oceans of Anxiety #230
metadata.description:
Fully generated by code on your machine. Variety of palletes and styles hand-picked with love and understanding.

Anxiety comes in waves.
It’s that sense of unidentifiable dread.
It can feel like you’re in the middle of an ocean on a rocking boat, and on those really bad days there isn’t even a lifebuoy, you’re drowning and can’t catch your breath, time is viscous and moving in slow-motion.

This piece does not set out to necessarily convey only the worst of dealing with anxiety, but also the resolutions and relief when it’s not there, or finally lets you go.
